the main data source for the melatonin measurements is the plasma samples taken from the birds at 4 time points across the day and night, with 5 birds per group sampled over a 14-day period. the melatonin levels were measured using an elisa kit as described in the paper.

the main data source for the melatonin values reported in this paper is the experimental setup and melatonin measurement procedures described in the franke et al. (2015), but with additional light intensity treatments.
